      "text": [
        "اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِي مَا تَقَرَّبْتُ بِهِ إِلَيْكَ بِلِسَانِي ثُمَّ خَالَفَهُ قَلْبِي."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "My Allah forgive me that with what I sought nearness to Thee with my tongue but my heart opposed and did not perform it."
        ]
      }
    },
